question: List all university students and college students studying Business Administration.
sql_query1:
SELECT Students.FullName
FROM Students
WHERE (Students.HigherEducationInstitution = "University" OR Students.HigherEducationInstitution = "College") AND Students.AcademicProgram = "Business Administration"
sql_query2:
SELECT Students.FullName
FROM Students
WHERE Students.HigherEducationInstitution = "University" OR Students.HigherEducationInstitution = "College" AND Students.AcademicProgram = "Business Administration"
interpretation1: Which university students study Business Administration and which college students have the same academic program?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all university students and also provide a list of college students studying Business Administration.
